Hey, there. Let's go.

00:07:10.221 --> 00:07:11.765 position:50% align:center
Yeah.

00:07:23.068 --> 00:07:25.111 position:50% align:center
[TEACHER A] We're going to have
another quiz next week,

00:07:25.195 --> 00:07:28.073 position:50% align:center
so if you don't review this
part, you may very well

00:07:28.156 --> 00:07:32.744 position:50% align:center
regret it. All right.
That's it for today.

00:07:40.710 --> 00:07:42.879 position:50% align:center
[YU]
Ayumu!

00:07:42.962 --> 00:07:44.047 position:50% align:center
Wait long?

00:07:44.130 --> 00:07:45.757 position:50% align:center
[AYUMU]
Nah. You ready to go?

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:49.260 position:50% align:center
Before we do, would you mind
if we stopped somewhere first?

00:07:49.344 --> 00:07:50.345 position:50% align:center
Please?

00:07:50.428 --> 00:07:53.014 position:50% align:center
[AYUMU]
Hm? Sure. I don't mind.

00:07:53.098 --> 00:07:54.724 position:50% align:center
You rock!

00:07:55.600 --> 00:08:01.648 position:50% align:center
Huh...? Hang on!

00:08:01.731 --> 00:08:03.775 position:50% align:center
Hey! Where are we going?

00:08:03.858 --> 00:08:05.902 position:50% align:center
The School Idol Club,
where else?

00:08:05.985 --> 00:08:09.656 position:50% align:center
[gasps] Wait, Yu.

00:08:11.741 --> 00:08:15.036 position:50% align:center
I'm not sure.

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:17.622 position:50% align:center
You know, school idols were
a complete mystery to me

00:08:17.706 --> 00:08:20.333 position:50% align:center
before now. But then yesterday,

00:08:20.417 --> 00:08:22.669 position:50% align:center
I went home and watched
a ton of videos!

00:08:22.752 --> 00:08:24.462 position:50% align:center
Uh?

00:08:24.546 --> 00:08:26.589 position:50% align:center
[YU] They're as cool
as they are cute.

00:08:26.673 --> 00:08:31.302 position:50% align:center
And they shine just like stars.
Every last one of them!

00:08:31.386 --> 00:08:35.306 position:50% align:center
They... grabbed my heart
right outta my chest!

00:08:35.390 --> 00:08:37.934 position:50% align:center
Remember the girl we saw
performing yesterday?

00:08:38.018 --> 00:08:40.103 position:50% align:center
Her name's Setsuna Yuki,
and I love her!

00:08:40.186 --> 00:08:41.229 position:50% align:center
Love?!

00:08:41.312 --> 00:08:43.523 position:50% align:center
It turns out that
she's pretty famous.

00:08:43.606 --> 00:08:45.608 position:50% align:center
She's known as the
mysterious school idol

00:08:45.692 --> 00:08:48.820 position:50% align:center
from Nijigasaki High!
I wonder if she has a fan club.

00:08:48.903 --> 00:08:51.823 position:50% align:center
Well, all I know is I've gotta
see her perform again!

00:08:51.906 --> 00:08:52.949 position:50% align:center
Hang on.

00:08:53.033 --> 00:08:54.492 position:50% align:center
Don't forget that
we're second-years.

00:08:54.576 --> 00:08:56.870 position:50% align:center
I thought that we were gonna
go to prep school together.

00:08:56.953 --> 00:08:59.831 position:50% align:center
We should focus on that,
not chasing some school idol.

00:08:59.914 --> 00:09:01.416 position:50% align:center
[YU]
Two birds, one stone!

00:09:01.499 --> 00:09:05.045 position:50% align:center
Here's what I mean, listening to
Setsuna's songs helped me study.

00:09:05.128 --> 00:09:06.796 position:50% align:center
Like, I even aced a quiz!

00:09:06.880 --> 00:09:09.966 position:50% align:center
So, I assure you,
it's not a waste of time!

00:09:10.050 --> 00:09:13.219 position:50% align:center
See? I just have so
much motivation now.

00:09:13.303 --> 00:09:15.555 position:50% align:center
Makes me feel like
I can do anything!

00:09:15.638 --> 00:09:17.182 position:50% align:center
[laughs]

00:09:18.975 --> 00:09:20.101 position:50% align:center
[laughs]

00:09:21.311 --> 00:09:24.981 position:50% align:center
Let's go get an autograph!
Or maybe two!

00:09:25.065 --> 00:09:27.108 position:50% align:center
Slow down!

00:09:28.526 --> 00:09:32.113 position:50% align:center
[YU]
Whoa! All these rooms are clubs?

00:09:32.197 --> 00:09:34.532 position:50% align:center
This is our first
time here, isn't it?

00:09:34.616 --> 00:09:36.284 position:50% align:center
[YU]
It's huge!

00:09:36.368 --> 00:09:38.536 position:50% align:center
[AYUMU]
So, which way do we go to get to

00:09:38.620 --> 00:09:41.456 position:50% align:center
the Idol Club room,
anyway? Do you know?

00:09:41.539 --> 00:09:43.583 position:50% align:center
[YU]
Sadly, I do not.

00:09:43.667 --> 00:09:46.378 position:50% align:center
Nobody's bothered to update
the school homepage in a while,

00:09:46.461 --> 00:09:48.880 position:50% align:center
and it wasn't listed in
the directory, either.

00:09:48.963 --> 00:09:50.799 position:50% align:center
[AYUMU]
Then, what was your plan?

00:09:50.882 --> 00:09:53.551 position:50% align:center
To stop by each room
and ask till we find it!

00:09:53.635 --> 00:09:55.011 position:50% align:center
[AYUMU]
Really?

00:09:55.095 --> 00:09:58.098 position:50% align:center
It's fine.
How long could it take?

00:09:58.181 --> 00:10:01.142 position:50% align:center
[AYUMU]
You're kidding me!

00:10:01.226 --> 00:10:02.435 position:50% align:center
Hi.

00:10:02.519 --> 00:10:04.938 position:50% align:center
Hi, welcome to the
Nagashi Somen Club!

00:10:05.021 --> 00:10:06.690 position:50% align:center
Are you wanting to join?

00:10:06.773 --> 00:10:08.024 position:50% align:center
Um. No thank you,

00:10:08.108 --> 00:10:10.318 position:50% align:center
but do you know where
School Idol Club meets?

00:10:10.402 --> 00:10:13.947 position:50% align:center
Can't say that I do, no.

00:10:14.030 --> 00:10:15.323 position:50% align:center
Looks tasty.

00:10:15.407 --> 00:10:17.117 position:50% align:center
Excuse us.

00:10:27.335 --> 00:10:29.337 position:50% align:center
[YU] This is harder
than I thought it'd be.

00:10:29.421 --> 00:10:32.298 position:50% align:center
[AYUMU] Our school does have
over a hundred clubs, you know.

00:10:32.382 --> 00:10:35.468 position:50% align:center
I can't believe you ever thought
it would be easy to begin with.

00:10:35.552 --> 00:10:37.595 position:50% align:center
Sorry, okay?

00:10:37.679 --> 00:10:38.972 position:50% align:center
[BOTH gasp]

00:10:39.055 --> 00:10:41.182 position:50% align:center
[YU]
Um. Excuse me.

00:10:41.266 --> 00:10:43.268 position:50% align:center
[RINA]
Hm?

00:10:43.351 --> 00:10:45.270 position:50% align:center
Are you familiar with
the School Idol Club?

00:10:45.353 --> 00:10:47.856 position:50% align:center
If so, do you know where it is?

00:10:56.990 --> 00:10:59.909 position:50% align:center
Maybe we caught her
at a bad time?

00:10:59.993 --> 00:11:02.412 position:50% align:center
Hey! What's going on, Rinari?

00:11:02.495 --> 00:11:05.415 position:50% align:center
Uh. Hey, Ai.

00:11:06.791 --> 00:11:09.044 position:50% align:center
